chaos-raid-no-more-threat-announcement-shuttle-call = Evacuation of all Facility personnel is underway! Evacuation transport is en route, estimated time of arrival: { $time } { $units }.
chaos-raid-no-more-threat-announcement = Evacuation shuttle is on its way. All Staff, report to the evacuation point immediately.

chaos-raid-rules-window =
    You are not mindless killers; you are a Chaos Insurgency soldier.
    Your absolute priority is your objectives, not slaughtering the entire personnel.
    Command expects you to execute your mission to the best of your ability, not to stage a bloodbath.
    Make sure to familiarize yourself with the Chaos Insurgency lore before you start playing.
    You can be punished for unjustified killings.
    The fewer casualties among civilian personnel, the better!
